\c 6
\s Micherechedzo mitanhatu yekutanga inozarurwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndakaona Gwayana parakazarura chimwe chemicherechedzo, ndokunzwa chimwe chezvisikwa zvipenyu zvina chichiti, senzwi remutinhiro: Uya uone.
\v 2 Zvino ndakaona, uye tarira, bhiza jena, naiye wakaritasva wakange ane uta; korona ndokupiwa kwaari, zvino akabuda achikunda, uye kuti akunde.
\v 3 Zvino rakati razarura mucherechedzo wechipiri, ndakanzwa chisikwa chipenyu chechipiri chichiti: Uya uone.
\v 4 Zvino kwakabuda rimwe bhiza dzvuku; newakaritasva akapiwa \add simba\add* kuti abvise rugare panyika, nekuti vaurayane; ndokupiwa kwaari munondo mukuru.
\v 5 Zvino rakati razarura mucherechedzo wechitatu, ndakanzwa chisikwa chipenyu chechitatu chichiti: Uya uone. Zvino ndikaona, uye tarira, bhiza dema, newakange akaritasva wakange ane chiyereso muruoko rwake.
\v 6 Zvino ndakanzwa inzwi pakati pezvisikwa zvipenyu zvina richiti: Chiyero chezviyo nedhenario*, nezviyero zvitatu zvebhari* nedhenario; nemafuta newaini usa\add zvi\add*tadzira.
\v 7 Zvino rakati razarura mucherechedzo wechina, ndakanzwa inzwi rechisikwa chipenyu chechina richiti: Uya uone.
\v 8 Zvino ndakaona, uye tarira, bhiza rakachenuruka, newakange akaritasva zita rake Rufu; uye hadhesi rakateverana naye. Simba ndokupiwa kwaari kuuraya kusvika pane chechina chenyika, nemunondo, uye nenzara, uye nerufu, uye nezvikara zvenyika.
\v 9 Zvino rakati razarura mucherechedzo wechishanu, ndakaona pasi pearitari mweya yevakange vaurawa nekuda kweShoko raMwari, uye nekuda kweuchapupu hwavaiva nahwo.
\v 10 Zvino vakadana nenzwi guru vachiti: Kusvikira rinhi, Tenzi, mutsvene uye wechokwadi, regai kutonga nekutsiva ropa redu pane vanogara panyika?
\v 11 Zvino kwakapiwa umwe neumwe nguvo  chena, zvikanzi kwavari vambozorora chinguva chiduku kusvikira vamwewo varanda pamwe navo nehama dzavo dzaiva dzoda kuurawa saivowo vakwaniswa.
\v 12 Zvino ndakaona parakange razarura mucherechedzo wechitanhatu, uye tarira, kwakava nekudengenyeka kwenyika kukuru, uye zuva rakasviba sesaga remvere, nemwedzi ukaita seropa;
\v 13 nenyeredzi dzedenga dzakawira panyika, semuonde unozuza maonde awo eshure, uchizuzwa nemhepo huru.
\v 14 Zvino denga rakabva serugwaro rwakapetwa; negomo roga roga nechiwi zvakabviswa panzvimbo dzazvo.
\v 15 Nemadzimambo enyika, nevanhu vakuru, navafumi, nevatungamiriri vehondo, nevane simba, nevaranda vose, nevakasununguka vose vakanozvivanza mumapako nemumabwe emakomo,
\v 16 zvino vakati kumakomo nekumabwe: Wirai pamusoro pedu, mutivige pachiso chaiye unogara pachigaro cheushe, nepakutsamwa kweGwayana;
\v 17 nekuti zuva guru rekutsamwa kwaro rasvika; zvino ndiani unogona kumira?
